        <b style="font-size: 100px;">Our mission.</b> <br><br>
        The COVID-19 pandemic has disproportionately affected many families by limiting room for an equitable learning environment. To tackle this challenge, we have created Matchbook Foundation, a non-profit organization for young students from affected families to connect with dedicated teachers from all over the world. Classes will be free, one-on-one or in groups (if requested), and held online.
      </div>

