      <div class="container-fluid" align="right">
        <b style="font-size: 100px;">How it works.</b> <br><br>
        We offer tutors in many courses, including math, sciences, languages, and music. Students can choose to receive help with a subject that they are currently learning in school (currently available for only math related topics) or with a supplementary subject to advance their knowledge. Students who choose the latter option will be instructed based on the course syllabus, specially planned by our Curriculum Managers. Each course is term contained: 12 classes, once per week. <br><br>

        After applying to be a mentee/mentor on the matchbookfoundation.org website, you will receive an email from our team notifying you of your login details for the matchbook.academy website if your application is approved. 
